snippet.title: Need for Speed Teaser Trailer - PC, PS4, Xbox One
snippet.description:
Subscribe to see the first full Need for Speed trailer on June 15th: http://bit.ly/1InsHgG

Need for Speed returns in Fall 2015 to PS4, Xbox One and PC in an action driving experience that unites the culture of speed

The new NFS game will feature deep customisation, authentic urban car culture, a nocturnal open world, and an immersive narrative that pulls you through the game.

Follow us:

Twitter: http://bit.ly/1H3gpbR 

Facebook: http://on.fb.me/1DVSlTH 

Instagram: http://bit.ly/1RjBmVN
